title: FRIDAY 2/26- Could Russell Wilson be on the move?
itunes:title: FRIDAY 2/26- Could Russell Wilson be on the move?
description:
Free agent JJ Watt (0:09) could be making a decision on his new team soon, while former teammate Deshaun Watson's (0:24) future in Houston is still up in the air. Seahawks quarterback Russell Wilson (1:02) has a host of team's inquiring about his availability. We'll hear from Wilson's teammate KJ Wright (1:18) about the QB's importance to the Seahawks. We have an update on Dak Prescott's future in Dallas and Chris Godwin (2:13) talks about the possibility of signing a Franchise Tag from the Buccaneers
